  <brief_title>The Effects of GIP and GLP-2 on the Secretion of Glucagon in Patients With Type 1 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of GIP and GLP-2 on the Secretion of Glucagon in Patients With Type 1 Diabetes</official_title>
