  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether Glucose-dependent Insulinotropic
      Polypeptide (GIP) or Glucagon Like Peptide 2 (GLP-2) has an affect on the secretion of
      Glucagon from the pancreas in patients with type 1 diabetes mellitus.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
