  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Caucasians over 18 years with type 1 diabetes (WHO criteria)

          -  Arginine test without rise in plasma C-peptide

          -  Normal blood Hemoglobin

          -  Informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Liver disease

          -  Diabetic nephropathy

          -  Treatment with medications unpausable for 12 hours
      </textblock>
